title: Westminster Dog Show 2017: Breed results, winners, Best in Show
text:
February 13, 2017 10:33pm   8:58pm EST The 141st Westminster Kennel Club Dog Show kicks into high gear Monday night at Madison Square Garden. Poodle runs during 2017 Westminster Dog Show (Getty Images) 
Updated at 10:33 p.m. ET 
Updated at 10:33 p.m. ET 
There are good dogs, and there are great dogs. Now it's time to crown the elite dogs. 
The 141st Westminster Kennel Club Dog Show kicks into high gear Monday night at Madison Square Garden. If you're looking for TV and streaming options to watch the show, we've got a handy guide right here . 
California Journey, a German shorthaired pointer, won Best in Show at last year's competition. Who will be Best in Show this time? Group Judging on Monday and Tuesday will determine which dogs get a chance at the coveted title. 
Group winners will be updated below as the results come in. Westminster Dog Show 2017 results Hound
